WEBVTT

00:12:01.625 --> 00:12:04.976
So is it possible

00:12:05.000 --> 00:12:07.893
that we could actually change the game

00:12:07.917 --> 00:12:10.768
by taking this very familiar plant

00:12:10.792 --> 00:12:15.143
and developing a nonaddictive,
FDA-approved medication

00:12:15.167 --> 00:12:17.375
for opioid use disorder?

00:12:19.000 --> 00:12:20.809
Absolutely.

00:12:20.833 --> 00:12:22.893
That is why we're working
so hard right now

00:12:22.917 --> 00:12:24.958
to develop a solution based on CBD.

00:12:26.125 --> 00:12:27.417
For me,

00:12:28.833 --> 00:12:32.708
the potential benefits
are obvious and also overwhelming.